{"type": "article", "id": 28124, "title": "Mango 推出孕妇装，以及，J.W.Anderson 春季系列不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-13T12:10:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 20894, "name": "唇膏"}, {"id": 11592, "name": "夏季"}, {"id": 1190, "name": "伦敦男装周"}, {"id": 7227, "name": "街拍"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 28895, "name": "格拉斯"}, {"id": 28896, "name": "日本百货"}, {"id": 3322, "name": "Givenchy"}, {"id": 6822, "name": "kinfolk"}, {"id": 28897, "name": "La Paz"}, {"id": 2009, "name": "Christian Louboutin"}, {"id": 15344, "name": "Mango"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 3350, "name": "Louis Vuitton"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 28898, "name": "Zlatan Ibrahimovic"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702165942LcZ3uszdt8ThWprx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/beams-japan-paris-pop-up-store\"><b>BEAMS 将在巴黎开“快闪店”</b></a>｜日本知名百货 BEAMS 将在巴黎开“快闪店”，6 月 21 日至 7 月 2 日，在 Marais  区的 White Coats  工作坊内，集中展示大批日本街头品牌。而 BEAMS  目前在上海、北京、香港、曼谷等地有门店。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Louis-Vuitton-fragrances-to-be-launched-in-September,701865.html\"><b>Louis Vuitton 发布新香水</b></a>｜法国奢侈品牌 Louis Vuitton 宣布九月将推出一个香水系列，名为 christened Les Parfums Louis Vuitton，这一系列早在 2014 年就开始筹备，而品牌上一次发布香水已经可以追溯到 1946 年。新香水背后的设计师为来自法国“香水之都”格拉斯的 Jacques Cavallier Belletrud，LV 聘请他之前，他曾为宝格丽工作。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/H-M-opens-first-store-in-Puerto-Rico,702238.html\"><b>H&amp;M 在波多黎各开了第一家店</b></a>｜H&amp;M 在波多黎各（Puerto Rico）开了第一家店，位于首都圣胡安，超过 1400 位顾客排队等待新店开幕。预计秋季将在波多黎各开第二家店。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Jones-New-York-to-close-all-37-Canadian-stores,702327.html\"><b>Jones New York 将关闭加拿大全部门店</b></a>｜美国女装零售商 Jones New York 近日宣布将关闭品牌在加拿大境内的全部 37 家门店，并申请债权人保护。去年 JNY 母公司就决定关闭加拿大所有门店，加拿大一家有百年零售历史的公司 Grafton Fraser  对其进行收购，近日法院裁定 Grafton Fraser 已无法支付账单。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Mango-launches-maternity-wear,701390.html\"><b>Mango 推出孕妇装</b></a>｜Mango 近日为准妈妈推出一个新系列，将于本周登陆线上及 86 个国家内的 158 家门店，共包含九件单品，牛仔、上衣、裙装和长袖衫，为顾客提供舒适和时髦的选择。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/givenchy-resort-2017-collection/\">Givenchy 2017 度假系列 lookbook</a> 前往意大利那不勒斯拍摄：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165920N2yPQUMAalRKh1nr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165921mqPGvJzM8dAsyIRB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165921ovemD8xT67XULHg2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165922k4nLBHGhNqRTA1VE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165922g3neA2RbqSMzuTLC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165923SgDqWf6Vns4Ce03I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165924digJ4KWEu1CnM3Nv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows/spring-2017-menswear/j-w-anderson\">J.W.Anderson 春季系列不错</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165924MWblt5s3LzUOXPdu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021659250SGhyRMnJINZv7VQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021659258HbXj1laAGxLO267.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165926DH1zCMjSqPlOA47L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165926g4QMHYlBKRALZIpV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165927e6hBNRVTD5fqUAQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165927gRYqLXrcIFKJpWuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165928GZKc1YWsuMqdgT3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165929TOwoNvRUYQpLmDdy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">此前我们预告过 </span><a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/httpwww-byrdie-comlouboutin-loubilaqueslide8/\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Christian Louboutin 再度推出新夏日唇膏系列</a><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">，更多细节图释出：</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"></span></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165929b6r78awnWkOMpRAv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165930gwa756Xp0cTS4FVq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165930jQhxcB1rmutSfFqI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">这里是本届伦敦男装周上著名街拍摄影师 <a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/slideshow/13445586/street-style-london-menswear-spring-17/\">Phil Oh 的作品</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165931l5m6sjvon3H41POT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165931GbFj8hlrnA5y3LRH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165932Yvmw146xbUSJsXcG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165932AFmEt19sk2D43uPV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165933XcvIFthVxmM0Dr3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165933mxzAPyMhgC8VQ5d9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165934Hmf1xe5LPQb8rtgY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/madewell-beach-style-2016-july/\">Madewell 发布假日沙滩造型特辑</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165935lUViT5dNFPCoMez6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73684211\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165935mMEd8Gn5i7fuOPsv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165936Rdqnuv2EgUoKzfTw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165936EiLzmD8lTprBsotg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">葡萄牙品牌  La Paz 以高质量原料及奇趣设计风格闻名，近日<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/kinfolk-la-paz-2016-summer-collection\">与 Kinfolk 服装品牌合作推出夏日特别系列</a>，灵感来自 80 年代迈阿密的那种休闲、酷酷的氛围。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165937Xl837Do4GHPc2Ayb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165937i5wR4Htlp0gVfy8W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165938lBsi2CxjMe5DKJyt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165938mDjCy8XMEpq5hULn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021659398ghZqTvpcmyVGNnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>瑞典球星  Zlatan Ibrahimovic <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/zlatan-ibrahimovic-a-z-sportswear\">推出自己的运动品牌 A-Z</a>，</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702165939YbovAwxTn20FULjW.jpg\" alt=\"\"